lastfm.summary: "Come as You Are" is a song by the American grunge band Nirvana, written by frontman Kurt Cobain. It is the third song overall and second single from the band's second album Nevermind. It was the album's second most successful single, and the band's second American Top 40 hit in 1992. After its release as a single in March 1992, "Come as You Are" peaked at number 32 on the Billboard Hot 100; it was the band's second and last American Top 40 hit. The single stayed on the chart for 18 weeks. Read more on Last.fm.
lastfm.title: Come as You Are
